Manage the AGH daemon

Usage:
  agh daemon [command]

Available Commands:
  start       Start the AGH daemon
  status      Show daemon status
  stop        Stop the AGH daemon

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for daemon

Global Flags:
  -o, --output string   Output format: human, json, or toon (default "human")

Use "agh daemon [command] --help" for more information about a command.
